@Node Description "Description"

  Description
  ===========

    The FileHistory door is a rather cool door that creates history files
    in LHA archives that detail the Time, Date, Handle and BBS that the file
    has ever been uploaded to.

    When a user uploads a file to the bbs we extract a file called:

    <Filename>.history     e.g. HBBSA10S.LHA.History

    We then add a line of text to the file that looks like this:

    Uploaded To <BBSName> by <Handle> on <Date> at <Time>

    e.g.

    Uploaded to Utopia! by Hydra/LSD on 01-JUL-1999 at 04:09:20

    This lets users and sysops see what bbs is getting what files first.  This
    also lets people create top bbs/trader charts quite easily too!

@EndNode


@Node Installation "Installation"

  Installation
  ============

    This is included as part of the default HydraBBS setup.

    This door should be called when the system door Extract_DIZ door is called
    it is NOT meant to replace the existing Extract_DIZ door.

    Add the following lines to your SYSTEM command list file, changing the number
    2 in the example below to the number of the last ExtractDIZ door + 1.

    Extract_DIZ_Type_2=NORMAL
    Extract_DIZ_Door_2=HBBS:Doors/System/FileHistory/FileHistory.HBBS

    Then copy the file "FileHistory.HBBS" to HBBS:Doors/System/FileHistory

@EndNode

